```
@Embeddable
@Data
public class CompositeId implements Serializable {
    private Long id; // pk
    private String accountId; // sharding key
}

@Table("xxxx")
@Entity 
public class YourClass {
    @EmbeddedId
    private CompositeId compositeId;
}
```

